title.narrative: Multitranche Financing Facility (MFF) - Jammu and Kashmir Urban Sector Development Investment Program (Subproject 1)

description.narrative: The components proposed for financing under the Project are: A. Urban Infrastructure and Environmental Improvements 1. The Sindh canal raw water pipeline in Srinagar 2. Sewerage and drainage in Jammu 3. The solid waste disposal facility at Srinagar 4. BC Road widening and overpass in Jammu B. Capacity Building, Institutional Development, Governance and Investment Program Support
